 utm_source=artificialnouveaugrantdesk&utm_medium=referral
LOCATION:Berlin\, Germany. Premiered at CTM 2027 and broadcast on Deutschla
 ndfunk Kultur\, with onward broadcast via ORF Oe1 and musikprotokoll. No n
 ationality restrictions are stated\; the form asks for citizenship but exc
 ludes no nationality.
END:VEVENT
