BEGIN:VEVENT
UID:zamek-artist-residency-poznan-2027@artificialnouveau.github.io
DTSTAMP:20260722T163201Z
DTSTART;VALUE=DATE:20260727
DTEND;VALUE=DATE:20260728
SUMMARY:Deadline: ZAMEK Artist Residency 2027 (ZAMEK Culture Centre\, Pozna
 n)
DESCRIPTION:Open call for ZAMEK Culture Centre's 2027 Artist-in-Residence p
 rogramme in Poznan. Supports artists working across visual arts\, performa
 nce\, choreography\, dance\, music\, sound art\, architecture and filmmaki
 ng (literature is excluded). Two formats: a Conceptual Residency (creative
  stay\, no requirement to complete or present a final work\, with public m
 eetings at least every two weeks) and an Operational Residency (concluding
  with an artistic event such as an exhibition\, concert or screening\, plu
 s regular public meetings). Selected artists receive accommodation in the 
 former imperial residence\, a studio\, a fee of PLN 6\,000 gross per month
 \, a production budget of PLN 5\,000 to 15\,000 gross\, curatorial support
  and publicity. Residencies run 4 to 8 weeks in 2027. ZAMEK is particularl
 y interested in projects that engage changing realities\, the current mome
 nt and the future (climate and migration crises\, the war in Ukraine\, soc
 ial and political issues) or the context\, history and architecture of the
  Castle\; project scale must fit the programme budget\, and projects shoul
 d not rely on external co-financing. Download the Terms & Conditions on th
 e ZAMEK site to apply. Deadline: 27 July 2026.\n\nOrganisation: ZAMEK Cult
 ure Centre (Centrum Kultury ZAMEK)\nLocation: Poznan\, Poland\nAward: Acco
 mmodation in an apartment in the former imperial residence\, studio access
 \, a fee of PLN 6\,000 gross per month (contract for specific work)\, a pr
 oduction budget of PLN 5\,000 to 15\,000 gross depending on length of stay
  and project\, plus curatorial support and publicity. No application fee l
 isted.\nDuration: 4 to 8 weeks during 2027 (Conceptual or Operational Resi
